casebody.head_matter:
In the Matter of DISCIPLINE OF George Mark ZUGANELIS.
No. D-2884.
Supreme Court of the United States
March 21, 2016.
George Mark Zuganelis, of Harwood Heights, Illinois, is suspended from the practice of law in this Court and a rule will issue, returnable within 40 days, requiring him to show cause why he should not be disbarred from the practice of law in this Court.
